dmca.title: Disney Complains of Pirated "Pirates" Photos
dmca.body:
To Whom It May Concern:

I certify under penalty of perjury that I believe the following to be accurate and that I am authorized to act on behalf of the owner of exclusive rights that have been infringed by postings on and/or by hyperlinks from Internet web pages operated by Google, Inc. I am sending this notice on the basis of a good faith belief that the pages identified below include infringing material and/or links to infringing material that are not authorized by the copyright owner, its agents, or the law. Please act expeditiously to remove or disable access to the infringing materials described below.

Owner of the copyrighted works:

The Walt Disney Company, Disney Enterprises, Inc. and Walt Disney Pictures and Television (collectively "Disney")

Copyrighted works infringed upon:

Pre release publicity stills from the feature film Pirates of the Caribbean 2

Location of infringing material:
